com.dlsc.flexgantt.swing.layer

Interface ILayerContainerRowHeaderRenderer

  • All Superinterfaces:
    IRenderer, IRowHeaderRenderer<LayerContainerRowHeader>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    DefaultLayerContainerRowHeaderRenderer, DefaultResourceNodeRowHeaderRenderer, MacLayerContainerResourceRowHeaderRenderer, MacLayerContainerRowHeaderRenderer

    public interface ILayerContainerRowHeaderRenderer
extends IRowHeaderRenderer<LayerContainerRowHeader>
    An extension of the row header renderer used for rendering the row headers of each row inside a LayerContainerRowHeader component. This row header component is placed on the left-hand edge of the layer container and can be used for visualizing things like resource capacity scales.

    1.0
